high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room, then turn left and walk toward the microwave.
Open microwave, retrieve the fork inside microwave, and close the microwave.
Turn around to the left and go to the sink.
Rinse the fork in the sink.
With the fork, get out of kitchen, pass through the sofa in living room, and head toward the drawer with lamp on it.
Store the fork in the top drawer of the chest end table.

Turn left and walk few step to the fork.
Get the fork from the sink.
Turn around and walk few steps and turn left and put the fork on the sink for wash.
Wash the fork and put it back in the drawer. Then turn around and walk towards the living room.
Put the fork on the Living room table drawer it was place on the corner.

Take the fork from the microwave.
